00035 unsigned int KX_Hash(void * inDWord)
00036 {
00037 #if defined(_WIN64) && !defined(FREE_WINDOWS64)
00038     unsigned __int64 key = (unsigned __int64)inDWord;
00039 #else
00040     unsigned long key = (unsigned long)inDWord;
00041 #endif
00042 
00043     key += ~(key << 16);
00044     key ^=  (key >>  5);
00045     key +=  (key <<  3);
00046     key ^=  (key >> 13);
00047     key += ~(key <<  9);
00048     key ^=  (key >> 17);
00049 
00050     return (unsigned int)(key & 0xffffffff);
00051 }
